WordAndPOSDictionaryLabellingStrategy - Class in opennlp.ccg.parse.supertagger
A `labelling strategy' for a CCG supertagger that restricts the output of the model based on word and POS `tagging dictionaries' in the following way: if a word w occurs at least K times in training, the model's output is constrained to the outcomes seen with w during training.
